Package sk.stu.fiit.logic

Class Building

java.lang.Object
sk.stu.fiit.logic.Building
public class Building
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a building that has to be cleaned. Also, use the WeekDays class to know even more details.

      public Building​(java.lang.String city, java.lang.String street, java.lang.String houseNumber, java.lang.String description, double timeNeeded, WeekDays primaryDay, boolean[] secondaryDays, int offset, int periodicity)
      Parameters:
      city - represents the city, where is located an exact building
      street - represents the street, where is located an exact building
      houseNumber - represents the street number of the building
      description - contains some details about the building
      timeNeeded - represents the time when should be cleaned
      primaryDay - represents the best day for cleaning
      secondaryDays - represents all possible days for cleaning
      offset - represents the week when the work should be started
      periodicity - represents the cleaning regularity
